{"tid":2215124,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［深度遊］一家64口，預約左去海洋公園玩，想日日去","createTime":"2020-09-23T18:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T17:31:00.000Z","uid":210366,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1964abecfba16839b2794ab6bbc9c64d6b32faa2","tid":2215124,"uid":210366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T18:43:07.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>無預約唔入海洋公園架</strong></span></span><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">約滿即止，手快有，手慢無</span></strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">記得先預約，去到現場先買飛</span></strong></span><br />\n自從疫情開始，大家都無乜去過街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如大家一齊預約去海洋公園？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一家4口，連埋魚缸60條魚，預約左64位<br />\n星期一至星期日都預約左，<br />\n希望每日都可以入場玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z9CuqkA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ9CuqkA.png&h=b7f1e21a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s8z8FTV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs8z8FTV.png&h=90d04a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5yPD27g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5yPD27g.png&h=9ca586ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K304edX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK304edX.png&h=a009084e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0db5e31307128e976658b5187210c5c41cd36268","tid":2215124,"uid":210366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T18:44:04.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">此風不可助長<br />\n大家唔好賣預約比藍絲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nGydR0N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/th